                     <interp inst="t18221204-164-person1411" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a shopman to Mr. Sowerby, a pawnbroker, in St. John-street. The prisoner pawned the watch in the name of G. Walker, about nine o'clock in the morning. Callow came in about it directly after.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221204-164-person1412">
                  JOHN 
                  TWEEDY
               <interp inst="t18221204-164-person1412" type="surname" value="TWEEDY"></interp>
