                     <interp inst="t18221204-164-person1412" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 18th of November, about eight o'clock in the evening, I was sent for - I asked the prisoner for the duplicate of the watch - he pretended to look for it, and said he lost it in Holborn. I took him.</p>
